<td style="border-width: 2px; border-color: #008000; border-style: solid; border-right: none; border-left: none; background-color: #339966;" height="26" valign="top" width="73">
<p><b>Formato</b></p>
</td>
<td style="border-width: 2px; border-color: #008000; border-style: solid; border-right: none; border-left: none; background-color: #339966;" height="26" valign="top">
